    <h1>FAQs</h1>

<div class=FAQ_Header>Do I need to be on Facebook to
purchase tickets or to host events?</div>

No. The store is accessable on the entire internet. Only the administrator of the store needs facebook.
<br /><br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>How do people get to my Groupstore?</div>

Go to the "My Events" page, you will see at the top
a link to your Groupstore.  It should look like "http://www.theGroupstore.com/nameofyourgroup".  
Your guests can find your store at that link.
<br /><br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>How do I know who bought a ticket?</div>

Find the event on the "My Events" page, and click on "Guest List".
That will have a list of everyone who bought a ticket to that event.
<br />
