<div class=FAQ_Header>Why do you use PayPal for the
transactions?</div>

PayPal is the safest way to sell anything online. Currently the service has registered 153 million accounts
in 190 markets. PayPal has received over 20 awards for internet excellence. For more information about PayPal and how it works please visit <a
