<div class=FAQ_Header>How do I set up a PayPal account?</div>

In order to receive ticket
sales, you must have a PayPal merchant account. This account is free and can
easily be set up at <a
href="https://www.paypal.com/ca/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_pro-nonpro-welcome&amp;from_ppip=wp_standard">https://www.paypal.com/ca/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_pro-nonpro-welcome&amp;from_ppip=wp_standard</a>.
<br />
<br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>How do I add administrators
to my Groupstore?</div>

On the navigational bar, go to
“settings” and click on “admin”. You can then add anyone on your Facebook Friends list as an administrator of your store.

<br />
<br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>Is there a fee for free events?</div>

No there is no charge to run a free event on Groupstore.
<br />
<br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>Do my guests need a PayPal to
purchase tickets?</div>

No, tickets can be bought with Paypal, Mastercard or Visa.
<br />
<br />
<div class=FAQ_Header>How do I change the details of an
event (ticket price, ticket classes)?</div>

Find the event on the "My Events" page, and click on "Edit".

